windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: Docks created with ObjectDock can be used to store programs, folders, files, and active processes. It also supports animations when the user rolls the cursor over the dock.
NOTE: Support for the DockZip format was added in ObjectDock 1.5.

description: Custom dock created with ObjectDock, a program that creates a dock for the Windows desktop (similar to Mac OS X); includes icons and background images used by the dock; saved in a compressed archive format.
